import Swiper from"swiper";import{Navigation,Pagination}from"swiper/modules";import"swiper/css";import"swiper/css/navigation";import"swiper/css/pagination";function initWooapbCarousels(root=document){const elements=root.querySelectorAll(".wooapb-carousel");elements.forEach(el=>{"true"!==el.dataset.swiperInit&&(new Swiper(el,{modules:[Navigation,Pagination],slidesPerView:3,spaceBetween:20,navigation:{nextEl:el.querySelector(".swiper-button-next"),prevEl:el.querySelector(".swiper-button-prev")},pagination:{el:el.querySelector(".swiper-pagination"),clickable:!0}}),el.dataset.swiperInit="true")})}export default initWooapbCarousels;